          "q": "What access and download facilities does the IFEDI venue in Ciudad Real offer?",
          "a": "IFEDI is a modern venue that has large ground-level gates for the direct unloading of heavy materials and fair structures. This greatly facilitates assembly and optimizes setup time in the exhibition halls."
